---
title: Warm Pesto Roasted Autumn Veg and Bacon Salad with Oregano Potatoes and Greek Style Salad Cheese
description: Fall in love with salads again with our Warm Pesto Roasted Autumn Veg and Bacon Salad. Courgette, bell pepper, potatoes and baby plum tomatoes give this dish Mediterranean inspired autumnal flavour whilst still getting your veg in.
